# ü¶∏‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è Superheroes API

This is a Flask-based RESTful API for managing superheroes, their powers, and how strong each hero is with a particular power. Built as part of a coding challenge, this project demonstrates working with models, relationships, serialization, and CRUD operations using Flask and SQLAlchemy.

---

## üìå Features

- View all heroes and powers
- View detailed info for a single hero or power
- Assign powers to heroes with strength levels
- RESTful routes following standard HTTP methods
- JSON responses compatible with provided Postman collection

